# {{lb|en|star}} A group of stars (and possibly smaller bodies such as planets or asteroids) that orbit one another.
# {{lb|en|film}} A method of creating, promoting and exploiting [[movie star]]s in cinema, emphasizing on their images rather than acting.

===Usage notes===
Systems with planetary bodies orbiting stars are referred to as “[[solar system]]s” or “[[planetary system]]s”.

